        "description": {
            "value": "<p>A hag long ago cursed your family, or you are a descendant of a hag or changeling, and their accursed corruption infests your blood and soul.</p>\n<p><strong>Spell List</strong> occult</p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Skills</strong> Deception, Occultism</p>\n<p><strong>Granted Spells</strong> cantrip <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Daze]</em>, 1st: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Illusory Disguise]</em>, 2nd: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Stupefy]{Touch of Idiocy}</em>, 3rd: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Blindness]</em>, 4th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Outcast's Curse]</em>, 5th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Mariner's Curse]</em>, 6th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Cursed Metamorphosis]{Baleful Polymorph}</em>, 7th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Warp Mind]</em>, 8th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Spiritual Epidemic]</em>, 9th: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Nature's Enmity]</em></p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Spells</strong> initial: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Jealous Hex]</em>, advanced: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Horrific Visage]</em>, greater: <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.You're Mine]</em></p>\n<p><strong>Blood Magic</strong> Spiteful curses punish your foes. You deal 2 mental damage per spell level (basic Will save) to the first creature that deals damage to you before the end of your next turn.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feat-effects.Item.Effect: Hag Blood Magic]</p>"
        },
